    <!-- include if transitional -->
    <p class="section">
      <span class="indent-1">Your employment is on a transitional basis with an expected End Date on or around #End_date#. If you remain continuously employed by the Company in good standing through the End Date and, at the end of your employment, you sign a release of claims in a form substantially similar to that attached as Exhibit A, you will be eligible for a transition bonus of $#transition bonus# (the “Transition Bonus”), less applicable taxes and withholdings.  Further, during your eBay employment, you will be eligible for the same employee benefits available to other similarly-situated eBay employees and subject to the same eligibility requirements set forth in the plans.</span>
    </p>

    <div class="section">
