    <p class="section">
      <span class="indent-1">
        Upon your signature below, this will become our binding agreement with respect to your employment, its terms merging and superseding in their entirety all other or prior offers, agreements and communications, whether written or oral, by you and eBay as to the specific subjects of this letter.
      </span>
    </p>

    <p class="section">
      <span class="indent-1">
        We are excited at the prospect of you joining our team. Your background and qualifications will add a unique strength to eBay, as well as to our continued success. We look forward to having you on board!
